name: RD Dark Blue
description: Dark blue eye friendly version of Racedepartment.
css:
@-moz-document domain("www.racedepartment.com") {
.mainContainer,
.tabs li.active a,
.tabs.noLinks li.active,
.redactor_toolbar,
.pember_products_view {
    background-color: #23232d;
}
#content .pageContent {
    padding-top: 0px;
}
a:link,
a:visited,
.featuredWidget li .title a,
.tabs li a,
.tabs.noLinks li {
    color: #607D8B;
}
.redactor_toolbar li.redactor_btn_group ul {
    box-shadow: none;
}
.titleBar,
.breadcrumb,
.resourceListMain,
.resourceListItem .resourceImage,
.resourceListItem,
.resourceListItem .resourceStats,
.sidebar .secondaryContent,
.xengallerySideBar .secondaryContent,
.featuredWidget li .title,
.Menu .secondaryContent,
.secondaryContent,
.PageNav a,
.sectionMain,
.discussionListItem,
.XenBase .messageList .message,
#QuickSearchNav .primaryControls,
#QuickSearchNav .secondaryControls,
#QuickSearchNav .ctrlUnit.submitUnit,
#QuickSearchNav .blockLinksList,
#QuickSearchNav #commonSearches,
.search_form .xenForm,
.search_form_post .xenForm,
.search_form_profile_post .xenForm,
.search_form_resource_update .xenForm,
.tag_search .xenForm,
.xengallery_search_form_media .xenForm,
.nflj_showcase_search_form .xenForm,
.nflj_sportsbook_search_form .xenForm ul,
.eventConatainer,
#DiscussionListOptionsHandle a,
.tagList .tag,
.itemGallery .toolAlbum .likeAlbum,
.itemGallery .toolAlbum .commentAlbum,
.itemGallery .toolAlbum li,
#forums .node.primaryContent,
.innerContent .rateBlock {
    background-color: #2c2c36;
}
.PageNav a,
.XenBase .message .messageUserBlock,
.Menu,
.textCtrl,
.pember_products_view {
    border: 1px solid #2c2c36;
}
.textCtrl:focus,
.textCtrl.Focus,
.avatar img,
.avatar .img,
.avatarCropper,
#AccountMenu .statusPoster textarea,
#QuickSearchNav .textCtrl,
#QuickSearchNav #commonSearches ul,
.innerContent .rateBlock {
    border: 1px solid #90A4AE;
}
.navTabs {
    font-size: 12px;
    border-top: none;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19), 0 6px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.23);
    background-color: #373744;
}
.search_form .xenForm,
.search_form_post .xenForm,
.search_form_profile_post .xenForm,
.search_form_resource_update .xenForm,
.tag_search .xenForm,
.xengallery_search_form_media .xenForm,
.nflj_showcase_search_form .xenForm,
.nflj_sportsbook_search_form .xenForm,
.tabs li a,
.tabs.noLinks li,
#DiscussionListOptionsHandle a,
.tagList .tag,
.tagList .tag .arrow:after,
.node .nodeLastPost,
.avatar img,
.avatar .img,
.avatarCropper {
    border: 1px solid #23232d;
}
.navPopup .PopupItemLinkActive:hover,
.navPopup .PopupItemLinkActive:hover,
.blockLinksList a:hover,
.blockLinksList a:focus,
.blockLinksList li.kbSelect a,
.blockLinksList label:hover,
.blockLinksList label:focus,
.blockLinksList li.kbSelect label,
.tabs li:hover a,
.tabs.noLinks li:hover,
.tagList .tag:hover {
    background-color: #373744;
}
.titleBar,
.breadcrumb .crust a.crumb,
.PopupControl,
.resourceList,
.resourceListItem .resourceStats dt,
.resourceListSidebar h3,
html,
body,
.PageNav a,
.sidebar .section .primaryContent h3,
.sidebar .section .secondaryContent h3,
.profilePage .mast .section.infoBlock h3,
.XenBase .xengallerySideBarContainer .xengallerySideBar .section h3,
.xenForm .ctrlUnit > dd .textCtrl,
#AccountMenu .statusPoster textarea,
.tabs li:hover a,
.tabs.noLinks li:hover,
.eventCell a:link,
.eventCell a:visited,
#DiscussionListOptionsHandle a,
.sectionFooter,
.tagList .tag,
.textHeading,
.xenForm .sectionHeader,
.itemGallery .toolAlbum a.control {
    color: #a7a7a7;
}
.muted,
.sidebar .section .primaryContent h3 a,
.sidebar .section .secondaryContent h3 a {
    color: #CFD8DC!important;
}
.actionFilterRow,
.resourceListItem,
.resourceListSidebar h3,
.discussionListItem,
tr.calendarevents,
.sidebar .section .primaryContent h3,
.sidebar .section .secondaryContent h3,
.profilePage .mast .section.infoBlock h3,
.XenBase .xengallerySideBarContainer .xengallerySideBar .section h3,
.primaryContent,
.sectionFooter,
.tabs,
.xbStickyBar,
.textHeading,
.xenForm .sectionHeader,
#forums .node.primaryContent {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #23232d;
}
.xenForm fieldset + .ctrlUnit,
.xenForm .formGroup + .ctrlUnit,
.xenForm .submitUnit {
    border-top: 1px solid #23232d;
}
.resourceList,
.sidebar .section .primaryContent h3,
.sidebar .section .secondaryContent h3,
.profilePage .mast .section.infoBlock h3,
.XenBase .xengallerySideBarContainer .xengallerySideBar .section h3,
html,
.discussionList .sectionHeaders,
.XenBase .message .messageUserBlock,
.bbCodeBlock,
.tabs li a,
.tabs.noLinks li,
.xenForm .ctrlUnit > dd .textCtrl,
.avatar img,
.avatar .img,
.avatarCropper,
.Menu .sectionFooter,
.Menu .primaryContent,
.primaryContent,
#AccountMenu .statusPoster textarea,
#QuickSearchNav .textCtrl,
.xbStickyBar,
.discussionList .sectionFooter,
.node .nodeLastPost,
.messageUserBlock .extraUserInfo,
.message .messageUserBlock div.avatarHolder,
.sectionFooter {
    background-color: #26262f;
}
.resourceListSidebar h3 {
    background-color: #26262f;
}
}
